    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I made these scones this morning. They came out tasty, but the dough was very, *very* sticky. I was barely able to knead it. I aerated and sifted the flour before using it. The scones came out pretty good, but very flat, like a thick focaccia. Did I miss something? Is the dough supposed to be that sticky?</p>
    </div>

